Followers Reports Privacy Policy 

INTRODUCTION 

For a better experience, while using our Service, we may require you to provide us with certain personally identifiable information, including but not limited to Instagram login, Instagram password. The information that we request is will be retained by us and used as described in this privacy policy. Instagram login, Instagram password save locally on device and not transmitted to third parties. Instagram login, Instagram password use only for login to Instagram, get information about profile and following to user. You also agree with Instagram Privacy Policy.  

We use third-party analytics tools to help us measure traffic and usage trends for the Service. These tools collect information sent by your device or our Service, including the web pages you visit, add-ons, and other information that assists us in improving the Service. 

We never share your Instagram password with any third party or store it in any of our servers. All this information is stored locally on your android device and is deleted permanently as soon as you log out or uninstall the app.  


